data.name: LanguageCountryInfo
desc: The language and country identifiers and descriptive names of the loaded locale data returned by XLocaleData.getLanguageCountryInfo().

items.name: Country
lines: ISO-3166 country code, for example, \"US\" or \"DE\".

items.name: CountryDefaultName
lines: Descriptive country name, for example, \"United States\" or \"Germany\".

items.name: Language
lines: ISO-639 language code, for example, \"en\" or \"de\".

items.name: LanguageDefaultName
lines: Descriptive language name, for example, \"English\" or \"German\".
